<section class="section-sm">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="row g-5">
			<div class="col-lg-4 mb-5 mb-lg-0">
				<div class="bg-white shadow rounded-lg p-4 sticky-top" style="top: 30px;">
					<h4 class="has-line-end">{{ service.name }}</h4>
					<nav id="TableOfContents">
						<ul>
							<li><a href="#how-it-works">How It Works</a>
								<ul>
									<li><a href="#key-features">Key Features</a>
									</li>
								</ul>
							</li>
							<li><a href="#benefits">Benefits</a>
							</li>
							<li><a href="#get-started">Get Started</a>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</nav>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-lg-8">
				<div class="content">
					
					<!-- SERVICE 1: BUDGET MANAGEMENT -->
					{% if id == 1 %}
					
					<h2 id="how-it-works">How Budget Management Works</h2>
					<p>Fin-Dinari's Budget Management system uses AI-powered technology to automatically categorize your transactions and provide real-time insights into your spending habits. Track every dinar you earn and every cent you spend across multiple wallets including Cash, Bank Accounts, Crypto, and Investments.</p>
					<p>Our intelligent system learns your spending patterns and helps you identify areas where you can save. Set monthly budgets for different categories like groceries, entertainment, transportation, and utilities, and receive alerts when you're approaching your limits.</p>
					
					<h3 id="key-features">Key Features</h3>
					<ul>
						<li><strong>AI-Powered Categorization</strong> - Automatically sorts your expenses into smart categories</li>
						<li><strong>Multi-Wallet Support</strong> - Manage Cash, Bank, Crypto, and Investment accounts in one place</li>
						<li><strong>Real-Time Balance Updates</strong> - See your financial position instantly across all accounts</li>
						<li><strong>Recurring Transaction Scheduling</strong> - Automate regular bills and income tracking</li>
						<li><strong>Spending Insights & Reports</strong> - Visual charts showing where your money goes</li>
					</ul>
					<hr>
					
					<h2 id="benefits">Benefits of Budget Management</h2>
					<div style="position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden;">
						<iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/jgAsPXRhTLQ" style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border:0;" allowfullscreen title="Budget Management Video"></iframe>
					</div>
					<hr>
					
					<h2 id="get-started">Get Started with Budget Management</h2>
					<p>Getting started is easy. Simply connect your bank accounts or start adding transactions manually. Our AI will learn your patterns and provide personalized recommendations to help you save more and spend smarter. Premium users get unlimited wallets and advanced analytics.</p>
					<p>Start tracking your finances today and take the first step toward financial freedom. Whether you're living paycheck to paycheck or building wealth, our budget management tools adapt to your unique situation.</p>
					
					
					<!-- SERVICE 2: LOAN INVESTMENT -->
					{% elseif id == 2 %}
					
					<h2 id="how-it-works">How Loan Investment Works</h2>
					<p>Fin-Dinari's Loan Investment feature transforms you from a spender to an investor. You can lend money to trusted borrowers, generate secure digital receipts, and earn returns after a fixed period. Your money works for you while helping others achieve their financial goals.</p>
					<p>Choose your investment amount, select the duration (1 to 12 months), and set your expected return rate. Our platform handles all documentation, receipts, and payment tracking automatically. When the loan matures, your principal plus earned interest is returned directly to your wallet.</p>
					
					<h3 id="key-features">Key Features</h3>
					<ul>
						<li><strong>Peer-to-Peer Lending</strong> - Connect directly with verified borrowers</li>
						<li><strong>Digital Receipts</strong> - Every transaction generates a secure, timestamped receipt</li>
						<li><strong>Fixed Return Periods</strong> - Choose 1, 3, 6, or 12 month investment terms</li>
						<li><strong>Return on Investment Calculator</strong> - See exactly what you'll earn before investing</li>
						<li><strong>Auto-Reinvest Option</strong> - Compound your returns automatically</li>
					</ul>
					<hr>
					
					<h2 id="benefits">Benefits of Loan Investment</h2>
					<div style="position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden;">
						<iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/jgAsPXRhTLQ" style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border:0;" allowfullscreen title="Loan Investment Video"></iframe>
					</div>
					<hr>
					
					<h2 id="get-started">Get Started with Loan Investment</h2>
					<p>Start with as little as 100 Dinar. Browse available loan requests, review borrower profiles and ratings, then choose where to invest. Our platform handles payment collection and will automatically credit your account when loans mature. Premium investors get priority access to high-rated borrowers and lower fees.</p>
					<p>Build your investment portfolio, earn passive income, and watch your wealth grow - all while helping others achieve their financial dreams.</p>
					
					
					<!-- SERVICE 3: OBJECTIVE MANAGEMENT -->
					{% elseif id == 3 %}
					
					<h2 id="how-it-works">How Objective Management Works</h2>
					<p>Fin-Dinari's Objective Management system helps you turn your financial dreams into reality. Set any goal - whether it's saving for a vacation, buying a car, building an emergency fund, or achieving financial independence. Our AI helps you create a realistic plan and keeps you motivated throughout your journey.</p>
					<p>Define your target amount, deadline, and how much you can contribute monthly. Our system calculates exactly when you'll reach your goal and suggests adjustments if you fall behind. Visual progress trackers and milestone celebrations keep you engaged and motivated.</p>
					
					<h3 id="key-features">Key Features</h3>
					<ul>
						<li><strong>Multiple Goal Types</strong> - Short-term (vacation, emergency fund), Medium-term (car, wedding), Long-term (retirement, children's education)</li>
						<li><strong>Visual Progress Trackers</strong> - See your progress with motivational animations</li>
						<li><strong>AI-Optimized Savings Plans</strong> - Get smart suggestions to reach goals faster</li>
						<li><strong>Catch-Up Mode</strong> - AI recalculates contributions if you fall behind</li>
						<li><strong>Milestone Celebrations</strong> - Congratulations at 25%, 50%, 75%, and 100%</li>
					</ul>
					<hr>
					
					<h2 id="benefits">Benefits of Objective Management</h2>
					<div style="position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden;">
						<iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/jgAsPXRhTLQ" style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border:0;" allowfullscreen title="Goal Management Video"></iframe>
					</div>
					<hr>
					
					<h2 id="get-started">Get Started with Objective Management</h2>
					<p>Setting your first goal takes less than a minute. Choose what you want to achieve, set your target amount and deadline, and our AI will create a personalized savings plan. Share your goals with the community for accountability, find an accountability partner, and celebrate every milestone along the way.</p>
					<p>Premium users can set unlimited goals, access advanced analytics, and connect with mentors who have achieved similar objectives.</p>
					
					
					<!-- SERVICE 4: COMMUNITY -->
					{% elseif id == 4 %}
					
					<h2 id="how-it-works">How Our Community Works</h2>
					<p>Fin-Dinari's Community transforms personal finance from a lonely journey into a shared adventure. Connect with like-minded individuals, learn from successful investors, and grow your financial knowledge together. Share your wins, ask questions, and celebrate milestones with people who understand your journey.</p>
					<p>Our platform includes social feeds, interest-based groups, mentorship programs, and monthly challenges. Whether you're interested in stock trading, crypto investing, real estate, or the FIRE movement, you'll find your tribe here.</p>
					
					<h3 id="key-features">Key Features</h3>
					<ul>
						<li><strong>Social Feed</strong> - Share financial wins, post questions, celebrate milestones</li>
						<li><strong>Interest-Based Groups</strong> - FIRE Movement, Stock Investors, Crypto Traders, Real Estate, Student Finances, Family Budgeting</li>
						<li><strong>Mentorship System</strong> - Learn from experienced investors and financial experts</li>
						<li><strong>Monthly Challenges</strong> - Compete in savings challenges and investment competitions</li>
						<li><strong>Accountability Partners</strong> - Get matched with someone who shares your goals</li>
						<li><strong>Billionaire Insights</strong> - Learn strategies from the world's most successful investors</li>
					</ul>
					<hr>
					
					<h2 id="benefits">Benefits of Joining Our Community</h2>
					<div style="position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden;">
						<iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/jgAsPXRhTLQ" style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border:0;" allowfullscreen title="Community Video"></iframe>
					</div>
					<hr>
					
					<h2 id="get-started">Get Started with Our Community</h2>
					<p>Join thousands of users who have transformed their financial lives with Fin-Dinari. Create your profile, introduce yourself in the welcome forum, join groups that match your interests, and start connecting. Share your first financial win, ask a question, or find an accountability partner today.</p>
					<p>Premium members get full access to all groups, mentorship opportunities, and can create their own private groups for family or close friends.</p>
					
					{% endif %}
					
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

{% endblock %}